WHICH LICENSE SHOULD YOU CHOOSE?
================================

Choose AGPL if:
‚úÖ Your project is open source
‚úÖ You're comfortable sharing all source code
‚úÖ You want to contribute back to the community
‚úÖ You're doing research or education
‚úÖ Your use is non-commercial

Choose Commercial License if:
üíº You're building a commercial product
